{"article_id":"0KM0Gl4lyE3nfvEe","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In a raucous campaign-style rally in Mississippi on Tuesday night , Donald Trump mocked Christine Blasey Ford ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"who in wrenching testimony at a hearing before the Senate judiciary committee last week said","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"the supreme court nominee Brett Kavanaugh had sexually assaulted her","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"when she was a teenager .","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"As hundreds of supporters cheered ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Trump delivered a crude imitation of Ford from her testimony ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"in which she vividly described a violent sexual assault","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"she alleges","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"Kavanaugh committed against her in the early 1980s ,","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"while admitting","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"that certain details of the time and place were lost to memory .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"Early on Wednesday , the Republican senator Jeff Flake , a key member of the Senate judiciary committee","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"that held the hearing ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"called Trump ' s remarks \" kind of appalling \" .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Trump has been accused of sexual misconduct by at least 20 women ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"whose allegations he has denied and dismissed .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"But last week he called Ford a \" very credible witness \"","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"and said :","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"\" I thought","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"her testimony was very compelling","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"and she looks like a very fine woman to me , very fine woman . \"","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"At his rally , the president mocked Ford ' s testimony with a question-and-answer patter","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that brought cheers from the crowd in Southaven , Mississippi .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"\" How did you get home ? \"","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"echoing a question","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Ford was asked by the committee .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"\" I don ' t remember , \"","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"the president said .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"\" How did you get there ? '","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"I don ' t remember.","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"' Where is the place ? '","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"I don ' t remember.","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"' How many years ago was it ? '","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"I don ' t know.","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"' What neighborhood was it ? '","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"I don ' t know.","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"' Where ' s the house ? '","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"I don ' t know . ' \"","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"Trump defends Kavanaugh","depth":4},{"id":40,"text":"but says","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"' a lot will depend ' on FBI investigation","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"Read more","depth":3},{"id":43,"text":"Trump concluded the riff","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"by lamenting the personal cost to Kavanaugh of Ford ' s allegations","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"and by insinuating","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"that Ford was part of a partisan conspiracy .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"\" They destroy people ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"these are really evil people , \"","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"\" To discuss something this sensitive at a political rally is just not right .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"It ' s just not right ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"and I wish","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"he had not done it , \"","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Flake said on NBC .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"He was standing next to the Democratic senator and fellow committee member Chris Coons of Delaware .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Flake triggered an FBI investigation of Kavanaugh last Friday","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"when , at the last minute","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"and after being confronted by two protesters in an elevator on Capitol Hill ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"he agreed to advance Kavanaugh ' s nomination","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"but only if there was a week delay for law enforcement to investigate allegations of serious sexual misconduct against the judge .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"The White House then ordered the investigation .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Flake made his about-face","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"having signaled moments earlier","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"that he would vote to approve Kavanaugh outright ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"then huddling in frantic negotiations with Democratics on the committee .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"He has since continued his strong stance","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"of questioning Kavanaugh ' s nomination .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"On Tuesday night after the remarks , Michael Bromwich , a member of Ford ' s legal team , condemned \" a vicious , vile and soulless attack \" .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Writing on Twitter ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"he said of Ford , and Trump :","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"\" Is it any wonder that she was terrified to come forward ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"and that other sexual assault survivors are as well ?","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"She is a remarkable profile in courage .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"He is a profile in cowardice . \"","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"Michael R. Bromwich","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"( @ mrbromwich )","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"A vicious , vile and soulless attack on Dr. Christine Blasey Ford .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Is it any wonder that she was terrified to come forward ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"and that other sexual assault survivors are as well ?","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"She is a remarkable profile in courage .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"He is a profile in cowardice .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"https : //t.co/UJ0bGxV1EZ","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"Last week ' s day of drama had followed an extraordinary hearing by the committee the day before","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"when Kavanaugh and Ford gave dueling testimony about a party in their high school years","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"at which","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"Ford says","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"the then 17-year-old Kavanaugh attempted to rape her ,","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"when she was 15 .","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"He furiously disputed the account in an emotional and partisan display .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"In contrast to Trump ' s portrayal on Tuesday evening , Ford accurately placed multiple people in Kavanaugh ' s contemporaneous social circle","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"- as established by his archived calendars from the era -","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"at the scene ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"and gave a clear account of the alleged attack itself .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"In her testimony , she said :","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"\" I am here today","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"not because I want to be .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"I am terrified .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"I am here","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"because I believe","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"it is my civic duty to tell you what happened to me","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"while Brett Kavanaugh and I were in high school . \"","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"Kavanaugh is Trump ' s second pick","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"to fill a supreme court vacancy .","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"The confirmation process for Trump ' s first pick , Neil Gorsuch , proceeded to a vote","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"without significant controversy .","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"Hundreds of law professors sign letters","depth":5},{"id":108,"text":"rejecting Kavanaugh nomination","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"Read more","depth":4},{"id":110,"text":"But Kavanaugh has been waylaid by accusations of sexual assault by Ford and two other women","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"who have spoken out publicly ,","depth":5},{"id":112,"text":"and by doubts about his testimony before the Senate ,","depth":5},{"id":113,"text":"which included conspiracy-mongering and dubious descriptions of his high school and college years .","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"Speaking under oath before the Senate committee ,","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"Kavanaugh denied any drinking problem","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"and denied bragging about sexual conquests in a high school yearbook entry .","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"Former classmates have since stepped forward","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"to say","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"that Kavanaugh was a frequent drunk .","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"The New York Times on Tuesday published a handwritten letter by Kavanaugh","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"instructing friends","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"participating in an upcoming holiday rental","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"to \" warn the neighbors","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"that we ' re loud , obnoxious drunks with prolific pukers among us \" .","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"In testimony last Thursday , Ford described attending a house party in the Washington DC suburbs in the early 1980s","depth":6},{"id":126,"text":"at which she was pushed into a bedroom","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"where a drunk Kavanaugh held her down ,","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"groped her ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"tried to strip her","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"and left her fearing for her life .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"Ford told the Senate","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"she was \" 100 % \" certain","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"that he was her attacker ,","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"Kavanaugh said","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"he was \" 100 % \" certain","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"he was not .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":273,"left":239,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","